        "content": "<p class=\"neanes-paragraph-style-default-text\"><span style=\"color:#C80831;font-family:Valkyrie OT,Neanes;font-style:italic;font-weight:400;\">Verse:</span> From the ends of the earth unto Thee have I cried. I will dwell in Thy tabernacle unto the ages. <span style=\"color:#C80831;\">(</span><span style=\"color:#C80831;font-family:Valkyrie OT,Neanes;font-style:italic;font-variant-numeric:oldstyle-nums proportional-nums;font-weight:400;\">Psalm 60:2a and 60:4a</span><span style=\"color:#C80831;\">)</span></p><p class=\"neanes-paragraph-style-default-text\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"neanes-paragraph-style-default-text\"><span style=\"color:#C80831;font-family:Valkyrie OT,Neanes;font-style:italic;font-weight:400;\">Verse:</span> I shall be sheltered in the shelter of Thy wings. For Thou, O God, hast heard my prayers. <span style=\"color:#C80831;\">(</span><span style=\"color:#C80831;font-family:Valkyrie OT,Neanes;font-style:italic;font-variant-numeric:oldstyle-nums proportional-nums;font-weight:400;\">Psalm 60:4b–5a</span><span style=\"color:#C80831;\">)</span></p><p class=\"neanes-paragraph-style-default-text\"><br><span style=\"color:#C80831;font-family:Valkyrie OT,Neanes;font-style:italic;font-weight:400;\">Verse:</span> So will I chant unto Thy Name unto the ages, that I may pay my vows from day to day. <span style=\"color:#C80831;\">(</span><span style=\"color:#C80831;font-family:Valkyrie OT,Neanes;font-style:italic;font-variant-numeric:oldstyle-nums proportional-nums;font-weight:400;\">Psalm 60:8</span><span style=\"color:#C80831;\">)</span></p>",
